veloper Day (February 2026)**\n- **Date**: February 20, 2026\n- **Focus Topics**: \n  - GitHub Copilot Coding Agent\n  - Plan Agent & Custom Agent in GitHub Copilot\n  - VS Code 1.07 version release\n  - Visual Studio 2026: Intelligent Development Environment\n- **Source**: Microsoft Developer Events\n\n### 2. **AI Agent Trends for 2026**\nSeveral sources indicate that **2026 is being viewed as a \"watershed year\" for AI agents**, particularly:\n- **From \"Talkers to Doers\"**: 2026 marks the transition from conversational AI to action-oriented agents\n- **Agent capabilities becoming industry standard**: What was premium in 2025 (Claude Code, Cursor, Devin) will become standard even in free tools\n- **Multi-agent collaboration**: Multiple specialized agents working together like real development teams\n\n### 3. **Tools Mentioned**\n- **GitHub Copilot Coding Agent** (enhanced agent mode)\n- **Claude Code** (launched Feb 2025, continuing evolution)\n- **OpenClaw** (predicted to exceed 200K stars by Q2 2026)\n- **Azure Cloud Agent Development Platform 3.0**\n\n---\n\n**Note**: To find specific ProductHunt launches from February 2026, you would need to visit ProductHunt.com directly and filter by date, as the search tool I have access to did not return ProductHunt results despite the domain filter.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
